{"tid":1819030,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[冷知識2.0]到底點樣先會中武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-01-10T12:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T12:40:03.000Z","uid":283868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f43b5c47bcb2e9b1148a516f1810302c9a86eb2c","tid":1819030,"uid":283868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:04:18.000Z","msg":"港共政權到而加都未查倒武漢肺炎係飛沫傳播定係空氣傳播<br />\n喺HA Standard ，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一般未確定到用咩媒介傳播</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都會以最高規格空氣傳播(Airborne)去處理病人嘅</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以我地只可以預先科普定大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>疾病傳播主要有三個媒介</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkLKKWw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkLKKWw.jpg&h=be2a2835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以下係人話翻譯<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">A. 接觸傳播 (Contact)  </span></strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你直接摸到啲病毒細菌又就咁食落個肚或者掂到黏膜</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">(所以要洗手）</span><br />\n<br />\n預防措施標準<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k4QbpU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk4QbpU4.jpg&h=31f66219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><strong>B. 飛沫傳播 (Droplet)</strong></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一個人咳或者打乞嗤<br />\n你呼吸系統直接吸入左嗰啲好細嘅口水鼻涕</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">(如果你見到人咳就唔好直接望住佢<br />\n或者帶返個口罩檔檔啲口水鼻涕)</span><br />\n<br />\n預防措施標準<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5TuC4Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5TuC4Va.jpg&h=3caaf077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nC. 空氣傳播 (Airborne)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">啲細菌由個病人呼出嚟<br />\n細菌病毒又痴住啲塵 <br />\n而你又吸左啲塵入肺</span><br />\n<br />\n但係一般呢啲情況都唔會有太大量細菌病毒 <br />\n除非你係一個空氣唔流通嘅情況下同嗰個病人相處太耐<br />\n<br />\n或者嗰個病人同你個距離好近<br />\n<br />\n都會提高做過病毒份量<br />\n(假如你覺得你身邊嘅人係有病嘅話你就唔好同佢相處一個空間太耐)<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">所以當年停課<br />\n其實應該停埋工</span><br />\n預防措施標準<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vdbqumV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvdbqumV.jpg&h=5c995129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nReference:<br />\nTellier, R., Li, Y., Cowling, B. J., &amp; Tang, J. W. (2019). Recognition of aerosol transmission of infectious agents: a commentary. BMC Infectious Diseases, 19(1). doi: 10.1186/s12879-019-3707-y<br />\n<a href=\"https://bmcinfectdis.biomedcentral.com/track/pdf/10.1186/s12879-019-3707-y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbmcinfectdis.biomedcentral.com%2Ftrack%2Fpdf%2F10.1186%2Fs12879-019-3707-y&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=0e6f9e80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bmcinfectdis.biomedcentral.com/track/pdf/10.1186/s12879-019-3707-y</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n以上資料由光貨百貨提供<br />\n<br />\n我地光復百貨短期內有唔同廠出嘅防疫口罩上架(包括3M)<br />\n<br />\n盡我地所能係全港防疫嘅同時<br />\n以最低嘅價錢向大家出售<br />\n希望可以保障倒大家嘅健康<br />\n<br />\n同時我地亦有出售文具<br />\n有經濟困難嘅小朋友無論想要邊個類型嘅產品<br />\n都歡近PM我地<br />\n我地會盡量幫手<br />\n<br />\n光復百貨<br />\nFacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/光復百貨-108572403977310/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E7%99%BE%E8%B2%A8-108572403977310%2F&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=397ee806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/光復百貨-108572403977310/</a><br />\n<br />\nIG<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/gong.fuk.hk?igshid=p43ra3rwroa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fgong.fuk.hk%3Figshid%3Dp43ra3rwroa&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=d199aeb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/gong.fuk.hk?igshid=p43ra3rwroa</a><br />\n<br />\nTG channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/gwong_fuk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fgwong_fuk&d=rH9paZ2ORyePGAAUSKfbjd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=34ce2cca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/gwong_fuk</a>"},{"pid":"737168fc08d76ee288bca72719b78b16d24824b7","tid":1819030,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:05:11.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"4063f1c41749b98efc20409b9adf6bf9fa320284","tid":1819030,"uid":125107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:05:54.000Z","msg":"幫個P牌仔推"},{"pid":"e4c0485ae5c7707b51f2dcdc106b30a6a239a24c","tid":1819030,"uid":125107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:06:07.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b6c3ee1c8b8c3d26b7eb468e3cdf17dcdb35c0ad","tid":1819030,"uid":125107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:06:21.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"05cf438a7c9dd9a2f42fe00fd813083c2ceed516","tid":1819030,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680899ee487e424b3f995f98d24e454fd3bbb220","tid":1819030,"uid":125107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:08:19.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"b83deed1d527799c9fa36ff1d6fcfd4d0ddac8be","tid":1819030,"uid":125107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:08:33.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"154bdb2e1b2063b5eaebfb59087e8f68afd93c90","tid":1819030,"uid":125107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"14e2841db19d6f658e2d19704d7ea67713f5de69","tid":1819030,"uid":125107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:10:52.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"32931e415cc83b83927ddb5758e5